                  </hi>I am a green-grocer, and live in King-street, Is<lb></lb>lington. On the 23rd of May some bundles of rhubarb hung outside the door—I heard a noise, went out, and saw (he prisoner cross the road with a bundle of rhubarb under his arm—I went after him—he threw it down, and began to run—I called, "Stop thief, " and he was stopped and given to me.</p>
